{
  "chapter": 15,
  "chapter_summary": "本章交代玉玲珑这双玲珑玉手的来历与易容本事。马如龙明白俞五、大婉要借玉玲珑之手把他改扮成张荣发，藏入西城窄巷的小杂货铺。大婉坦言她与俞五相信马如龙被人陷害，并以他曾冒险救人为证，劝他相信正义终会昭雪。她又说明杂货铺环境、伙计老土的可靠与张荣发妻子的安排，引出谢玉宝的身份。后半章谢玉宝、俞五和玉玲珑相继登场，众人在饮酒谈笑间完成易容布局，也显出各自的机锋、情义与江湖旧事。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你们选择了这个地方，就因为这种地方是江湖人绝不会来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那些官差，全都看不见我们，只因为他们都有求于俞五，不能不放个交情给他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "对。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "因为我已被认定了是个心狠手辣的恶徒，已逼得无路可走，所以你们才替我想出了这法子，让我可以多活些日子。",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "不对。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "俞五相信你，我也相信你。我们都相信你是被人陷害的，我们也知道你绝不会躲在一个小杂货铺里苟且偷生。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你为什么要相信我？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为我相信一个刚杀了人的凶手，在自己逃命的时候，绝不会冒险停下来，从雪地里救起一个快要被冻死的女人。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "可是你自己一定也要相信，人世间还是有正义公道存在的，邪恶迟早必将灭亡，阴谋迟早必将败露，你受到的冤枉迟早总有一天会洗清。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只要你能有这种信心，暂时受点委屈，又算得了什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那个杂货铺在哪里？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "就在西城的一条窄巷里，你的主顾，都是些善良穷苦的小百姓，能吃饱饭，已经很不容易，所以，很少会管别人的闲事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你的那个伙计也姓张，别人都叫他老土，除了偶尔喜欢偷偷的喝两杯烧酒外，绝对是个可靠的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "他认不出他的老板已经换了个人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他的眼睛一向不好，耳朵也有点毛病？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "就算他认不出来，别人呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "别人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你是不是说他那个多病的老婆？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她是个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "其实你自己应该看得出的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我看得出？我几时看见过她。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "刚才你还看见过她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "难道刚才我看见的那个好像已经死了的女人，就是我的……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "难道她就是张荣发的老婆？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "本来不是的，现在却快要是了，就好像你本来不是张荣发，现在却快要变成张荣发一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她本来是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她本来究竟是个什么样的人？现在你难道还是连这一点都不肯告诉我？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在我如果还是不肯告诉你，好像就未免有点不近人情了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我知道这三个字，你用不着说得这么详细。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她是个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你以为我连她是男是女都看不出？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你一定也看得出我只不过是在故意拖延而已，因为我实在不知道究竟应该告诉你多少事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你能告诉我多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "好，我告诉你，今年她十九岁，大概还没有碰过男人，也没有被男人碰过。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她真的只有十九岁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "难道，你觉得她已经很老了？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她的人虽然不老，武功却很老，她穿过那道高墙时就好像穿过张薄纸一样，那种功力连九十岁的人都未必能练到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我的功力也不比她差，你是不是认为我也很老了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "武功不是死练出来的，一个人功力的深浅，跟他的年龄大小没有多大关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她的武功的确很高，你们知道的那些英雄大侠们，能胜过她的绝对不会超出十个，因为她不但有个好师父，而且几乎是一出娘胎就开始练武了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她的师父是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "只答应告诉你有关她的事，不是她师父的事。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "那么，我就不问。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她的脾气不太好，大小姐的脾气总是不太好的，如果发现自己忽然变成了一家破杂货店的老板娘，说不定会气得发疯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "她发疯的时候，会不会一刀把那杂货店的老板杀了……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这一点你可以放心，她不会杀了你的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "你怎么知道她不会？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为她有病，病得躺在床上，连站都站不起来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可是看起来也绝对不像是个杂货店的老板娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "现在不像，等一下就会像了，而且绝对跟原来那个老板娘完全一模一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "玉玲珑真有这么大的神通？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她有多大的神通，等一下你自己就会看出来了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "其实我倒并不十分想看。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "等她醒来时，已经躺在杂货店后面的小屋里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你当然就在她床边照顾她，因为你们是多年的恩爱夫妻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "可惜她自己一定不会承认的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "她当然不会承认，可是你要一口咬定她就是你的老婆，姓王，叫王桂枝，已经嫁给你十八年了。不管她怎么说，怎么闹，你都要一口咬定。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "到后来连她自己都一定会变得胡里胡涂，连自己都不知道自己是谁了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你总算明白了。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我只有一点不明白。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "我跟她无冤无仇，为什么要做这种事。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "因为这样做不但对你有好处，对她也有好处，也只只有这样做才能把你受的冤枉洗清，把这件阴谋揭穿。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你是个多么骄傲的人，这种事你本来绝不肯做的，这次你就算为了我，我一直信任你，你最少也该信任我一次。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "现在你又准备要我干什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "当然是要你去喝酒，俞五在这里，你也在这里，如果不让你们两个人先痛痛快快的喝几杯酒，岂非更不近人情？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我知道你喜欢女儿红，可惜这地方实在找不到这么多女儿红。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_wu",
      "text": "善酿也是好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我们先喝女儿红，再喝善酿。一人一坛女儿红喝下去之后，什么酒喝起来都差不多了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_da_wan",
      "text": "一人一坛，她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "这次我不喝，玉大小姐刚才还告诉我，女孩子酒喝得太多，不但容易老，而且容易上当。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们喝你们的酒，我做我的事。我虽然从不喝酒，可是，也绝不反对别人喝酒，而且很喜欢看别人喝酒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_wan",
      "speaker_name": "大婉",
      "listener": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "text": "有时候我也觉得看人喝酒比自己喝有趣得多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有的人一喝醉就会胡说八道，乱吵乱闹，有的人喝醉了反而会变成个木头人，连一句话都不说，有的人喝醉了会哭，有的人喝醉了会笑，我觉得很有趣。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "你喝醉了是什么样子？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "speaker_name": "马如龙",
      "listener": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我生平只见过两个真正可以算美男子的人，你就是其中之一，所以，你就算喝醉了，样子也不会难看的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wu",
      "speaker_name": "俞五",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "他喝醉了是什么样子，你很快就会看到的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "我只替别人易容，从来不替自己做这种事。因为我就算能让自己变得年轻些，就算能骗得到别人，也骗不过自己。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "玉玲珑",
      "listener": "char_ma_ru_long",
      "text": "骗别人的事我可能会做，骗自己的事我是绝不做的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 15,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 311
    }
  ],
